cff-version: 1.2.0
title: a2a-compliance
message: "Automated compliance testing for the Agent2Agent (A2A) protocol"
type: software
authors:
  - name: a2a-compliance contributors
abstract: >-
  A compliance test kit and validator for A2A (Agent2Agent) protocol
  endpoints. Covers agent card schema, JSON-RPC envelope, A2A method set
  (v0.3 and v1.0), and security checks (SSRF, TLS, CORS, redirect
  re-check).
repository-code: "https://github.com/UltraSkye/a2a-compliance"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - a2a
  - agent2agent
  - compliance
  - testing
  - tck
  - llm
  - protocol
  - security
